Privacy Policy
Privacy Policy for Barcode Scanner
- Price Finder
Thank you for using Barcode Scanner app! We take privacy very seriously. Here we describe how we collect and use any information when you use Barcode Scanner, and what special permissions are required by the App.
Use of Camera
Barcode Scanner needs to use your phone camera in order to scan barcodes. Barcode Scanner does not take pictures with the camera, or uses the camera in any other way.
Collection of Data
Barcode Scanner does not collect any personal information. We may collect the data
(
application logs) regarding your use of the Barcode Scanner app, such as the frequency of use, what features of the app you used, the brand and model of your phone, and the version of the phone Operating System. We do it for the purpose of catching the software bugs and improving the application.
Sharing of Data
We do not share any data with third parties.
Changes
We may revise this Privacy Policy from time to time, and will post the most current version here.
Contact
If you have any questions about Barcode Scanner, please contact us at mobileappsshop@gmail.com
